{"tid":296881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平將訪港視察港珠澳大橋及西九文化區","createTime":"2017-06-25T03:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T08:28:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b0ca630c65bdde922813f95fe9f49c94664134","tid":296881,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:56:25.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】國家主席習近平星期四到港訪問三天。<br />\n<br />\n新華社報道，習近平將於周四至周六來港，出席慶祝香港回歸20周年大會暨香港特別行政區第五屆政府就職典禮，並視察香港特別行政區。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，習近平會視察港珠澳大橋及西九文化區，並會到石崗軍營檢閱解放軍駐港部隊。"},{"pid":"fb237d44ef64dc9ee5206d0a89165200ae3c35f9","tid":296881,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=226082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D226082&d=9%2BZN6Ff8PaoQpbDbzc4Ei%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=51a8fa7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D226082&h=15ac5308\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=226082</a>"},{"pid":"8797e75229f50ef3573f260a1447ed0020f34c77","tid":296881,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:59:41.000Z","msg":"親自試打石屎槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1255e9195619096d5c957c08377d5f32d71ace","tid":296881,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"希望支近平 受返自己國家種的因<br />\n同隨便果班一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(垃圾qc 垃圾材料)"},{"pid":"28e5bd7acdce68ce437d563d3532f7e00540536f","tid":296881,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望支近平 受返自己國家種的因<br />\n同隨行果班一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(垃圾qc 垃圾材料)</blockquote>"},{"pid":"770abbbadceec3c760793e6073a916b